🗣️ Ask more questions than stating your dissatisfactions and remember not to argue with what comes out of your partner’s mouth because whatever she says is true to her. Try to understand why she’s saying what she’s saying, so you can get the answers you need.

🗣️ Use words that show you’re in this together (“let’s, we, us”)

🗣️ Leave the conversation with action steps you can both agree to take, not matter how small.
